
WIFI:
=====

/etc/network/interfaces
/etc/wpa.conf

WIFI-Scan:
   https://rasspberrypi.wordpress.com/2012/09/09/wifi-tools-for-raspberry-pi/



/etc/modprobe.d/8192cu.conf
    options 8192cu rtw_power_mgnt=0 rtw_enusbss=0
chown root.root
chmod 644 8192cu.conf


